<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Are we supposed to think that Lawrence is about to die in 9/11? I cried because I thought that was coming, and then it didn't happen, and I wondered if that was the author's intention or if I had made an unfounded assumption. <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
